title: 2018 FIFA World Cup Russia ticket prices by category
summary: This grouped bar chart represents 7 different Ticket Types on X-axis for 4 groups Cat 1, Cat 2, Cat 3, and Cat 4. On the Y-axis it shows their corresponding SOME LABEL.
Ticket Type Final (64) had the maximum SOME LABEL among all 4 groups, and it was for Cat 1. The minimum SOME LABEL was observed in Ticket Type Group matches (2 to 48) for Cat 4.
In Ticket Type Final (64), Cat 4 had the highest SOME LABEL among all 7 Ticket Types and it has the lowest SOME LABEL in Ticket Type Group matches (2 to 48).
There is a gap of 90.0 between the highest and lowest SOME LABEL found for Cat 4 in Ticket Type Final (64) and Group matches (2 to 48).
